title: UK Top 40 March 4 1989

March 4 1989. 

A right royal battle between Michael Jackson, Michael Ball and Billy Joel at the top. New entries from Deacon Blue, Donna Summer, Paula Abdul and more.

In this show he plays the entire top 20, some from the lower end of the chart, and a dip into the album chart of the week.

Two hours of fun, chat and music to bring back many memories
